thread.title: Jordan
thread.title_full: Avery WePrint Australia reviewed by Jordan

author: Jordan
title: Jordan
text: Print quality in terms of resolution and colour replication is excellent. Type even at very small point is crisp and the colour is rich almost RGB like. Only thing i would have liked is a sticky-er adhesive. works fine on high gloss surfaces but not so much on satin or matte finishes
